# PageModel (TanStack Query) RULES

## Responsibilities

- PageModel owns `useQuery`/`useMutation`.
- UI consumes PageModel outputs only (ViewState + handlers).
- UI must not import `modules/*/api` or `shared/api` directly.

## Types

- Avoid `any`. Use explicit generics:
  - `useMutation<TData, TError, TVariables>()`
- Query keys / invalidation remain feature-local (do not scatter in shared).
